jnxIfOtnMib.name: jnxIfOtnMib

revisions.description: Removed INDEX clause from unwanted places
This MIB module defines objects used for managing the OTN interface for Juniper products.
Added config to leave fist byte of TTI as NULL per the G.709 recommendation.
Removed INDEX clause from unwanted places
Added OTN table entries for handling sub-port in the interface name. With suffix OCH2
Added OTN Alarms and PM data.
